<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" package="co.infinum.goldfinger.example">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="16" android:targetSdkVersion="27" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_FINGERPRINT" />
	<application android:theme="resourceId:0x7f0b0005" android:label="Goldfinger" android:icon="res/drawable/ic_launcher.xml">
		<activity android:name="co.infinum.example.MainActivity">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<activity android:name="co.infinum.example.ExampleActivity" android:screenOrientation="portrait" />
		<activity android:name="co.infinum.example.RxExampleActivity" android:screenOrientation="portrait" />
	</application>
</manifest>
